M=math PI=M.pi At=125 xd={}yd={}hd={}td={} iN=input.getNumber iB=input.getBool oN=output.setNumber oB=output.setBool lead=property.getBool("lead while aiming manually") tagc=property.getNumber("Search mode") usdg=property.getBool("camara upside down") for i=1,At do table.insert(xd,0) table.insert(yd,0) table.insert(hd,0) table.insert(td,-i) end
tadd=0 tt=0 for i=1,At do tadd=tadd+td[i] tt=tt+td[i]^2 end S=screen SD=S.drawLine function clamp(x,d,u) if x<d then y=d elseif x>u then y=u else y=x end return y end function cader(x,y,h,w,d) SD(x,y,x,y+d)SD(x+w,y,x+w,y+d)SD(x,y+h,x,y+h-d)SD(x+w,y+h,x+w,y+h-d) SD(x,y,x+d,y)SD(x+w,y,x+w-d,y)SD(x,y+h,x+d,y+h)SD(x+w,y+h,x+w-d,y+h) end YAW=0 pitch=0 zom=0.35 zom1=0.35 yx=0 yy=0 yh=0 til=0 ttil=0 function onTick() dis=iN(1) hre=iN(3) vre=iN(4) cs=iN(5) GPSx=iN(6) GPSy=iN(7) tilt=iN(8) if usdg then tiltC=-tilt hre2=-hre vre2=-vre else tiltC=tilt hre2=hre vre2=vre end alts=iN(9) dis2=iN(10) AD=iN(11) WS=iN(12) zoom=iN(13) yawp=iN(14) tiltA=iN(15) if usdg then tiltA=-tiltA AD=-AD WS=-WS end tiltB=tiltC-tiltA on=iB(2) rAim=iB(3) and iB(4) radar=iB(4) search=iB(5)
if not radar then Tyaw=M.fmod(cs+5.5,1)-0.5 hdis=dis2*M.cos(tilt*2*PI) X=hdis*M.sin(-Tyaw*2*PI)+GPSx Y=hdis*M.cos(Tyaw*2*PI)+GPSy H=dis2*M.sin(tilt*2*PI)+alts if lead then VX=X-yx VY=Y-yy VH=H-yh yx=X yy=Y yh=H else VX=0 VY=0 VH=0 end TF=dis2<4000 if dis2<4000 then g=50 r=10 else g=10 r=100 end dis=dis2 else Tyaw=M.fmod(-hre2+cs+5.5,1)-0.5 Tpitch=vre2+tilt hdis=dis*M.cos(Tpitch*2*PI) x=hdis*M.sin(-Tyaw*2*PI)+GPSx y=hdis*M.cos(Tyaw*2*PI)+GPSy h=dis*M.sin(Tpitch*2*PI)+alts for i=At,2,-1 do xd[i]=xd[i-1] yd[i]=yd[i-1] hd[i]=hd[i-1] end xd[1]=x yd[1]=y hd[1]=h xadd=0 yadd=0 hadd=0 txd=0 tyd=0 thd=0 for i=1,At do xadd=xadd+xd[i] yadd=yadd+yd[i] hadd=hadd+hd[i] txd=txd+xd[i]*td[i] tyd=tyd+yd[i]*td[i] thd=thd+hd[i]*td[i] end X=(xadd*tt-tadd*txd)/(At*tt-tadd^2) Y=(yadd*tt-tadd*tyd)/(At*tt-tadd^2) H=(hadd*tt-tadd*thd)/(At*tt-tadd^2) VX=(At*txd-tadd*xadd)/(At*tt-tadd^2) VY=(At*tyd-tadd*yadd)/(At*tt-tadd^2) VH=(At*thd-tadd*hadd)/(At*tt-tadd^2) TF=dis~=0 end
zom5=radar and not (TF and rAim) if zoom==1 and zom1<1 and not zom5 then zom1=zom1+0.01 end if zoom==-1 and zom1>0.35 and not zom5 then zom1=zom1-0.01 end if zom5 then zom=0.35 else zom=zom1 end if not on then zom1=0.35 end
zoom2=clamp(0.1-(zom-0.35)*0.15385,0.001,1) if search and on and radar and not (TF and rAim) then PIT=-(M.fmod(tiltC-tagc+100.5,1)-0.5) YAW=-0.1 elseif on and not (TF and rAim) then if AD==1 then YAW=-zoom2 til=tiltC elseif AD==-1 then YAW=zoom2 else YAW=0 end if WS==1 and tiltC<0.24 then PIT=zoom2 ttil=0 elseif WS==-1 and tiltC>-0.08 then PIT=-zoom2 ttil=0 elseif ttil<30 then ttil=ttil+1 til=tiltC PIT=0 elseif ttil==30 then PIT=-(M.fmod(tiltC-til+100.5,1)-0.5)*10 end elseif on and TF and rAim then YAW=-hre*5 PIT=vre*5 ttil=0 else YAW=-(M.fmod(yawp+100.5,1)-0.5) PIT=-(M.fmod(tiltB+100.5,1)-0.5)end if iB(11) then oN(1,iN(16)) oN(2,iN(17)) oN(3,iN(18)) oN(4,iN(19)) oN(5,iN(20)) oN(6,iN(21)) oN(10,iN(22)) oN(11,iN(23)) oN(12,iN(24)) oN(13,iN(25)) oB(1,iB(12)) oB(2,iB(19)) oB(3,iB(13)) oB(4,iB(14)) oB(5,iB(15)) oB(6,iB(16)) oB(7,iB(17)) oB(8,iB(18)) oB(9,true) else oN(1,X) oN(2,Y) oN(3,H) oN(4,VX) oN(5,VY) oN(6,VH) oN(10,GPSx) oN(11,GPSy) oN(12,cs) oB(1,TF and on) oB(2,on) oB(3,iB(4)and iB(6)) oB(4,iB(10) and TF) oB(5,iB(8)) oB(6,iB(9)) oB(7,iB(7)) oB(9,false) end oN(7,YAW) oN(8,PIT) oN(9,zom)
end function onDraw() w=S.getWidth() h=S.getHeight() smyl=M.floor(h*0.46875) smxf=M.floor((w+(w-h))*0.26042) smyf=M.floor(h*0.26042) r360=h*3.75 w2=w/2 h2=h/2 if rAim then S.setColor(255,10,10) else S.setColor(10,255,10) end if radar then cader(smxf,smyf,smyl,smyl,5) if TF and Pdis~=0 and Ydis~=0 then cader(w2+hre2*r360-3,h2-vre2*r360-4,7,7,2) S.drawText(M.floor(w2+hre2*r360-5.5),M.floor(h2-vre2*r360-10.5),M.floor(dis+0.5)) end end if not radar then S.setColor(10,255,10) S.drawText(w2-8,h2-11,M.floor(dis+0.5)) S.drawCircle(w2,h2,5) S.setColor(r,g,10,200) S.drawLine(w2-3,h2,w2+4,h2) S.drawLine(w2,h2-3,w2,h2+4) end end

dis = {} yaw={} pitch={} for i=1, 8 do table.insert(dis, 0) table.insert(yaw, 0) table.insert(pitch, 0) end
function onTick()
for i=1,32,4 do dis[math.floor((i-1)/4+1)]=input.getNumber(i) yaw[math.floor((i-1)/4+1)]=input.getNumber(i+1) pitch[math.floor((i-1)/4+1)]=input.getNumber(i+2) end
min=dis[1] mini=1 for i=2,8 do if min > dis[i] and dis[i] ~= 0 then mini=i min=dis[i] end end
output.setNumber(1,dis[mini]) output.setNumber(3,yaw[mini]) output.setNumber(4,pitch[mini]) output.setBool(1,input.getBool(1)) end

tadd=0 tt=0 for i=1,At do tadd=tadd+td[i] tt=tt+td[i]^2 end S=screen SD=S.drawLine function clamp(x,d,u) if x<d then y=d elseif x>u then y=u else y=x end return y end function cader(x,y,h,w,d) SD(x,y,x,y+d)SD(x+w,y,x+w,y+d)SD(x,y+h,x,y+h-d)SD(x+w,y+h,x+w,y+h-d) SD(x,y,x+d,y)SD(x+w,y,x+w-d,y)SD(x,y+h,x+d,y+h)SD(x+w,y+h,x+w-d,y+h) end YAW=0 pitch=0 zom=0.35 zom1=0.35 yx=0 yy=0 yh=0 til=0 ttil=0 function onTick() Pdis=iN(1) Ydis=iN(2) hre=iN(3) vre=iN(4) cs=iN(5) GPSx=iN(6) GPSy=iN(7) tilt=iN(8) if usdg then tiltC=-tilt hre2=-hre vre2=-vre else tiltC=tilt hre2=hre vre2=vre end alts=iN(9) dis2=iN(10) AD=iN(11) WS=iN(12) zoom=iN(13) yawp=iN(14) tiltA=iN(15) if usdg then tiltA=-tiltA AD=-AD WS=-WS end tiltB=tiltC-tiltA on=iB(2) rAim=iB(3) and iB(4) radar=iB(4) search=iB(5)
if not radar then Tyaw=M.fmod(cs+5.5,1)-0.5 hdis=dis2*M.cos(tilt*2*PI) X=hdis*M.sin(-Tyaw*2*PI)+GPSx Y=hdis*M.cos(Tyaw*2*PI)+GPSy H=dis2*M.sin(tilt*2*PI)+alts if lead then VX=X-yx VY=Y-yy VH=H-yh yx=X yy=Y yh=H else VX=0 VY=0 VH=0 end

zoom2=clamp(0.1-(zom-0.35)*0.15385,0.001,1) if search and on and radar and not (TF and rAim) then PIT=-(M.fmod(tiltC-tagc+100.5,1)-0.5) YAW=-0.1 sml=5 elseif on and not (TF and rAim) then if AD==1 then YAW=-zoom2 til=tiltC elseif AD==-1 then YAW=zoom2 else YAW=0 end if WS==1 and tiltC<0.235 then PIT=zoom2 ttil=0 elseif WS==-1 and tiltC>-0.08 then PIT=-zoom2 ttil=0 elseif ttil<30 then ttil=ttil+1 til=tiltC PIT=0 sml=5 elseif ttil==30 then PIT=-(M.fmod(tiltC-til+100.5,1)-0.5)*10 sml=5 end elseif on and TF and rAim then if sml<12 then sml=sml+0.25 end YAW=-hre*sml PIT=vre*sml ttil=0 else YAW=-(M.fmod(yawp+100.5,1)-0.5) PIT=-(M.fmod(tiltB+100.5,1)-0.5) sml=5 end if iB(11) then oN(1,iN(16)) oN(2,iN(17)) oN(3,iN(18)) oN(4,iN(19)) oN(5,iN(20)) oN(6,iN(21)) oN(10,iN(22)) oN(11,iN(23)) oN(12,iN(24)) oN(13,iN(25)) oB(1,iB(12)) oB(2,iB(19)) oB(3,iB(13)) oB(4,iB(14)) oB(5,iB(15)) oB(6,iB(16)) oB(7,iB(17)) oB(8,iB(18)) oB(9,true) else oN(1,X) oN(2,Y) oN(3,H) oN(4,VX) oN(5,VY) oN(6,VH) oN(10,GPSx) oN(11,GPSy) oN(12,cs) oB(1,TF and on) oB(2,on) oB(3,iB(4)and iB(6)) oB(4,iB(10) and TF) oB(5,iB(8)) oB(6,iB(9)) oB(7,iB(7)) oB(9,false) end --if usdg then YAW=-YAW PIT=-PIT end oN(7,YAW) oN(8,PIT) oN(9,zom) end function onDraw() w=S.getWidth() h=S.getHeight() smyl=M.floor(h*0.46875) smxf=M.floor((w+(w-h))*0.26042) smyf=M.floor(h*0.26042) r360=h*3.75 w2=w/2 h2=h/2 S.setColor(10,255,10) if radar then cader(smxf,smyf,smyl,smyl,5) if TF and Pdis~=0 and Ydis~=0 then cader(w2+hre2*r360-3,h2-vre2*r360-4,7,7,2) S.drawText(M.floor(w2+hre2*r360-5.5),M.floor(h2-vre2*r360-10.5),M.floor(dis+0.5)) end end if not radar then S.setColor(10,255,10) S.drawText(w2-8,h2-11,M.floor(dis+0.5)) S.drawCircle(w2,h2,5) S.setColor(r,g,10,200) S.drawLine(w2-3,h2,w2+4,h2) S.drawLine(w2,h2-3,w2,h2+4) end end

CompassR = 0 HDGT = 0
function onTick() CompassR = input.getNumber(5) * -1 HDGT = math.floor(((360 + CompassR) % 1)*360) AmmoMain = math.floor(input.getNumber(26)) AmmoHMG = math.floor(input.getNumber(27)) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(10,10,10,200) screen.drawRectF(42,0,16,7) screen.drawRectF(0,80,52,18) screen.setColor(0, 175, 0, 250) screen.drawTextBox(43, 1, 15, 5, string.format('%03.0f',HDGT), 0, 0) screen.drawText(2, 82, "76MM:") screen.drawTextBox(26, 82, 10, 5, AmmoMain, 0, 0) screen.drawText(2, 90, "12.7MM:") screen.drawTextBox(35, 90, 15, 5, string.format('%03.0f',AmmoHMG), 0, 0) end

object.script:
ft=0 Eangle=0 ySGPSx=0 ySGPSy=0 ySalt=0 G=-30/3600 ttdy=0 aimt=0 iN=input.getNumber iB=input.getBool oN=output.setNumber oB=output.setBool pgN=property.getNumber pgB=property.getBool lmax=pgN("max turn left (deg)")/360 rmax=-pgN("max turn right (deg)")/360 umax=pgN("max turn up (deg)")/360 dmax=-pgN("max turn down (deg)")/360 vpm=pgN("yaw pivot") rest=pgN("reload state") spmu=pgN("Aim speed") usdg=pgB("turret upside down") ACY=pgN("accuracy")/1000 Delay=7.5 FOV=0.9 NP=0
M=math abs=M.abs sin=M.sin cos=M.cos tan=M.tan asin=M.asin atan=M.atan sqrt=M.sqrt pi2=M.pi*2 pi=M.pi log=M.log fmod=M.fmod floor=M.floor Delay=9
wtyp=pgN('Weapon Type') bal={{800,0.025,120},{1000,0.02,150},{1000,0.01,300},{900,0.005,600},{800,0.002,1500},{700,0.001,2400},{600,0.0005,2400}} wtyp=wtyp<1 and 1 or wtyp>#bal and #bal or wtyp velo=bal[wtyp][1] DRAG=bal[wtyp][2] lifes=bal[wtyp][3]
function th(x,y,z) return x>y-z and x<y+z end
function atan2(y,x)ans=0 if y~=0 and x~=0 then if 0<y and 0<x then ans=atan(y/x)elseif 0<y and x<0 then ans=pi+atan(y/x)elseif y<0 and x<0 then ans=-pi+atan(y/x)elseif y<0 and 0<x then ans=atan(y/x)end else if x==0 then if 0<y then ans=pi/2 else ans=-pi/2 end else if 0<x then ans=0 else ans=pi end end end return ans end
function clamp(x,d,u) if x<d then y=d elseif x>u then y=u else y=x end return y end
function Pc(x, pos)if pos<-0.0139 and x<0 then return 0 elseif pos>0.23611 and x>0 then return 0 end return x end
function range(dist,elv) w,h=dist*cos(elv*pi2),dist*sin(elv*pi2) a,t=elv,0 for i=1,10 do vx,vy=velo*cos(a),velo*sin(a) t=-log(1-DRAG*w/vx)/DRAG if t>lifes then return false end y=-30*t/DRAG+(30/DRAG+vy)*(1-math.exp(-DRAG*t))/DRAG if y>=h-0.1 then return true end a=a+(elv*pi2)-atan2(y,w)end return false end
function FlightY(Vo, tick)return (Vo-G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG)*(1-DRAG)/-DRAG*(1-DRAG)^tick+G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG*tick+(Vo-G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG)*(1-DRAG)/DRAG end
function FlightXTime(Vo,x)return -log(1-DRAG*x/Vo)/DRAG end function TCH(ST,VT) return floor(ST*20)==floor(VT*20)end function calc(x,y) DOWN=atan2(y,x) UP=clamp(DOWN+0.20944,-1.5707,1.5707) for i=1,10 do AVE=(UP+DOWN)/2 Vx=velo/60*cos(AVE) Vy=velo/60*sin(AVE) time=FlightXTime(Vx,x) Y=FlightY(Vy,time) if Y<y then DOWN=AVE else UP=AVE end end Vx=velo/60*cos((UP+DOWN)/2) ft=FlightXTime(Vx,x) Eangle=(UP+DOWN)/2 return 0 end function onTick() Cx=iN(1) Cy=iN(2) Calt=iN(3) CVx=iN(4) CVy=iN(5) CValt=iN(6) tGPSx=iN(7) tGPSy=iN(8) talt=iN(9) tcp=iN(10) SGPSx=iN(11) SGPSy=iN(12) Salt=iN(13) if usdg then tilt=-iN(14) tiltb=-iN(16) else tilt=iN(14) tiltb=iN(16)end on=iN(15)==1 and iB(1) Re=iN(17)==1 and iB(1) cpb=iN(18)
Rep=Re and (rest==1 or rest==3)or iB(7) Rey=Re and (rest==2 or rest==3)or iB(7)
SVx=SGPSx-ySGPSx SVy=SGPSy-ySGPSy SValt=Salt-ySalt t=0 Cx=Cx+SVx*Delay Cy=Cy+SVy*Delay Calt=Calt+SValt*Delay for i=0,15 do hdis=sqrt((Cx-tGPSx+(CVx-SVx)*t)*(Cx-tGPSx+(CVx-SVx)*t)+(Cy-tGPSy+(CVy-SVy)*t)*(Cy-tGPSy+(CVy-SVy)*t)) vdis=Calt-talt+(CValt-SValt)*t calc(hdis,vdis) t=ft end yaw1=(atan2(-(Cx-tGPSx+(CVx-SVx)*t),Cy-tGPSy+(CVy-SVy)*t)/pi2)-cpb pitch1=Eangle/(2*pi) if usdg then pitch1=-pitch1 end dis=sqrt((hdis-0)^2+(vdis-0)^2) if yaw1>0.5 then yaw2=yaw1-1 elseif yaw1<-0.5 then yaw2=yaw1+1 else yaw2=yaw1 end
ycp=tcp-cpb if yaw2>0 then yaw5=yaw2 else yaw5=yaw2+1 end if ycp>0 then ycp5=ycp else ycp5=ycp+1 end if th(pitch1,tilt,ACY)and th(yaw5,ycp5,ACY) then if aimt<60 then aimt=aimt+1 end else aimt=0 end aimc=aimt==60 if yaw2<lmax and yaw2>rmax then ttdy=0 ftdy=true else ttdy=ttdy+1 ftdy=false end tdirecx=pitch1<umax and pitch1>dmax rec=on and ttdy<60 and range(dis,pitch1) if rec and not Rep then pitch=(fmod(clamp(pitch1,dmax,umax)-tilt+100.5,1)-0.5) else pitch=(fmod(tiltb-tilt+100.5,1)-0.5)end if rec and not Rey then yaw=fmod(clamp(yaw2,rmax,lmax)-ycp+100.5,1)-0.5 else yaw=(fmod(-ycp+100.5,1)-0.5) end if usdg then yaw=-yaw end oB(1,rec and ftdy and aimc and not Re and (iB(4)or iB(3))) oB(2,iB(5)) oB(3,iB(7)) oB(4,aimc) oN(3,ycp) oN(4,yaw2+ycp5) oN(5,yaw5) oN(6,ycp5) oN(1,clamp(yaw*8,-spmu,spmu)*vpm) oN(2,clamp(pitch*5,-spmu,spmu)) ySGPSx=SGPSx ySGPSy=SGPSy ySalt=Salt end

function range(dist,elv) w,h=dist*cos(elv*pi2),dist*sin(elv*pi2) a,t=elv,0 for i=1,10 do vx,vy=velo*cos(a),velo*sin(a) t=-log(1-DRAG*w/vx)/DRAG if t>lifes then return false end y=-30*t/DRAG+(30/DRAG+vy)*(1-math.exp(-DRAG*t))/DRAG if y>=h-0.1 then return true end a=a+(elv*pi2)-atan2(y,w)end return false end
function FlightY(Vo, tick)return (Vo-G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG)*(1-DRAG)/-DRAG*(1-DRAG)^tick+G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG*tick+(Vo-G*(1-DRAG)/DRAG)*(1-DRAG)/DRAG end
function FlightXTime(Vo,x)return -log(1-DRAG*x/Vo)/DRAG end function TCH(ST,VT) return floor(ST*20)==floor(VT*20)end function calc(x,y) DOWN=atan2(y,x) UP=clamp(DOWN+0.20944,-1.5707,1.5707) for i=1,10 do AVE=(UP+DOWN)/2 Vx=velo/60*cos(AVE) Vy=velo/60*sin(AVE) time=FlightXTime(Vx,x) Y=FlightY(Vy,time) if Y<y then DOWN=AVE else UP=AVE end end Vx=velo/60*cos((UP+DOWN)/2) ft=FlightXTime(Vx,x) Eangle=(UP+DOWN)/2 return 0 end function onTick() Cx=iN(1) Cy=iN(2) Calt=iN(3) CVx=iN(4) CVy=iN(5) CValt=iN(6) tGPSx=iN(7) tGPSy=iN(8) talt=iN(9) tcp=iN(10) SGPSx=iN(11) SGPSy=iN(12) Salt=iN(13) if usdg then tilt=-iN(14) tiltb=-iN(16) else tilt=iN(14) tiltb=iN(16)end on=iN(15)==1 and iB(1) Re=iN(17)==1 and iB(1) cpb=iN(18)
Rep=Re and (rest==1 or rest==3)or iB(7) Rey=Re and (rest==2 or rest==3)or iB(7)
SVx=SGPSx-ySGPSx SVy=SGPSy-ySGPSy SValt=Salt-ySalt t=0 Cx=Cx+SVx*Delay Cy=Cy+SVy*Delay Calt=Calt+SValt*Delay for i=0,15 do hdis=sqrt((Cx-tGPSx+(CVx-SVx)*t)*(Cx-tGPSx+(CVx-SVx)*t)+(Cy-tGPSy+(CVy-SVy)*t)*(Cy-tGPSy+(CVy-SVy)*t)) vdis=Calt-talt+(CValt-SValt)*t calc(hdis,vdis) t=ft end yaw1=(atan2(-(Cx-tGPSx+(CVx-SVx)*t),Cy-tGPSy+(CVy-SVy)*t)/pi2)-cpb pitch1=Eangle/(2*pi) if usdg then pitch1=-pitch1 end dis=sqrt((hdis-0)^2+(vdis-0)^2) if yaw1>0.5 then yaw2=yaw1-1 elseif yaw1<-0.5 then yaw2=yaw1+1 else yaw2=yaw1 end
ycp=tcp-cpb if yaw2>0 then yaw5=yaw2 else yaw5=yaw2+1 end if ycp>0 then ycp5=ycp else ycp5=ycp+1 end if th(pitch1,tilt,ACY)and th(yaw5,ycp5,ACY) then if aimt<60 then aimt=aimt+1 end else aimt=0 end aimc=aimt==60 if yaw2<lmax and yaw2>rmax then ttdy=0 ftdy=true else ttdy=ttdy+1 ftdy=false end tdirecx=pitch1<umax and pitch1>dmax rec=on and ttdy<60 and range(dis,pitch1) if rec and not Rep then pitch=(fmod(clamp(pitch1,dmax,umax)-tilt+100.5,1)-0.5) else pitch=(fmod(tiltb-tilt+100.5,1)-0.5)end if rec and not Rey then yaw=fmod(clamp(yaw2,rmax,lmax)-ycp+100.5,1)-0.5 else yaw=(fmod(-ycp+100.5,1)-0.5) end if usdg then yaw=-yaw end oB(1,rec and ftdy and aimc and not Re and (iB(4)or iB(3))) oB(2,iB(5)) oB(3,iB(7)) oB(4,aimc) oN(3,ycp) oN(4,yaw2+ycp5) oN(5,yaw5) oN(6,ycp5) oN(1,clamp(yaw*8,-spmu,spmu)*vpm) oN(2,clamp(pitch*5,-spmu,spmu)) ySGPSx=SGPSx ySGPSy=SGPSy ySalt=Salt end
